data.Name: These Horses, Those Eels
data.Bio: Los Angeles CA via Portland OR, Portland OR via Los Angeles CA. This duo operates between both worlds. Robert E. Ward III brings guitar, vocals, bass, synths and programing to the equation. Jeffrey W. Mattson brings guitar, vocals, bass, synths and programing to complete the equation. Marinated in lo-fi and Seattle rock, these boys wear their influences like most people wear retainers: with purpose, poise, but not properly on display because thatâ€™d be gross.
